text: Hey! I am over it! I want to be able to see, speak to and hug another adult in real life and not a bloody zoom meeting. This is HARD! How are you? xx

Haha I know right! It’s day to day, sometimes good sometimes bad. I’m an over thinker so I have to find ways of getting out of my head ( naps are a natural reset for me ). Otherwise I’ve been productive with work and today we had our second to last assessment. Which is emotional because the end is nigh and we finish in 6 weeks . But otherwise I'm ok. How is it juggling work the kids? And is the online school thing working for them? xx
